of the more wealthy owners, land owners, in
Los Angeles was Abel Sterns and he had a party.

00:19:47.220 --> 00:19:52.400
He had the nicest place in Los Angeles and
he had a party and some party crashers showed

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:57.420
up and the way they handled that was they
just stuck rifles out the window and fired

00:19:57.420 --> 00:20:08.150
them until the crowd of the and that discouraged
them. It worked. Now, we've come to the first

