surveyed map of Los Angeles. This is Orin's
survey. This was done in 1949 and it's all

00:20:17.420 --> 00:20:24.850
about the money. So, the city realizes that
the American government wants them to pay

00:20:24.850 --> 00:20:32.840
taxes; the state of it is here and they don't
really have any money. So, they're gonna sell

00:20:32.840 --> 00:20:41.730
city lands and they are gonna measure it exactly.
You can see on here, originally the settlers

00:20:41.730 --> 00:20:49.120
who came here, the 44 original settlers. Actually,
two of them were deemed too lazy and they

