00:21:05.170 --> 00:21:13.680
The streets had to be a plaza of a certain
size. The lots were only like, 40 by 90 and

00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:19.140
this is something that happened and continued
to happen right up into the 20th Century.

00:21:19.140 --> 00:21:24.770
They would name the cities in both Spanish
and English. So you see Calle Loma, that's

