00:34:27.211 --> 00:34:35.380
building, and in a city like this with like
60 thousand people. So, they had to build

00:34:35.380 --> 00:34:40.710
roads, they had to bring in gas lines and
they to figure out something to do with this

00:34:40.710 --> 00:34:47.401
sewage. So this is a map that was used in
